http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Shastri%E2%80%99s-principles-lauded/article14014892.ece

Sunil Shastri, son of the former Prime Minister Lal Bahadur Shastri, has said that the moral lessons taught by his father have left an everlasting impression on his mind.He was here on Friday to inaugurate a youth awareness programme to commemorate the 119th birth anniversary of Netaji Subhas Chandra Bose. It was organised by the Basava Seva Samsthe.Mr. Shastri, who lived all his life on the principles of simplicity and truthfulness, was a great source of motivation. His slogan ‘Jai Jawan Jai Kisan’ in support of farmers and soldiers was remembered even today. He called upon the students to set a goal and work hard to achieve them.